{"tid":1922881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙士香港人「感謝支那出錢出力」；武漢肺炎西人「感謝支那出錢出力」","createTime":"2020-03-12T22:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T22:37:08.000Z","uid":63822,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8ca3fa5404b472c26286fe91409327d7a97cf6","tid":1922881,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:15:13.000Z","msg":"好心故技重拖都搵個成功例子<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係睇唔到今日既香港係反共方便係世界第一？<br />\n<br />\n定真係咁短視，呃得一日得一日，諗住之後彈弓反彈再算<br />\n<br />\n唔洗長時間，過幾日啦，到支那捐既口罩入到西方平民手中，佢地就可以感受到紙咁薄既「誠意」<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係睇得出點解正名咁重要<br />\n<br />\n叫coronavirus，佢地拎到made in Wuhan既口罩都仲懞性性<br />\n<br />\n如果叫Wuhanvirus就知自己仆街中伏<br />\n<br />\n唔知痰菜duck真係咁撚醒定無意啦，支那又佔到便宜<br />\n<br />\n感覺班西人幾年後就可以體驗我地而家既感受<br />\n<br />\n話需如此輿論都係要打<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家入去幫班西人認清事實「支那輸出病毒、隱瞞疫情，事後假惺惺想呃光環」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/calvert_3/status/1237702234634412033?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcalvert_3%2Fstatus%2F1237702234634412033%3Fs%3D21&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f41f1eff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcalvert_3%2Fstatus%2F1237702234634412033%3Fs%3D21&h=c97d254a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/calvert_3/status/1237702234634412033?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"172a099f0ed5d246cdcdd4c740190bc30fded9e2","tid":1922881,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://twitter.com/calvert_3/status/1237702234634412033?s=21\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcalvert_3%2Fstatus%2F1237702234634412033%3Fs%3D21&h=e80d1597&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"085caaaf653822fea0455d44fb157a8fb98ab6a9","tid":1922881,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.me.me/the-wuhan-corona-virus-68616711.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%